OL,3,CPolitician concerned over Jersey's
OL,4,Cborder authority if UK law introduced
OL,6,FJersey's former Bailiff has raised
OL,7,Fconcerns that the island could risk
OL,8,Finadvertently passing responsibility
OL,9,Ffor control of its borders to the UK.
OL,11,FSir Philip Bailhache's comments come
OL,12,Fahead of next week's States sitting,
OL,13,Fwhere a proposition looking to extend
OL,14,Fa section of the UK's Nationality and
OL,15,FBorders Act (2022) to cover Jersey
OL,16,Fwill be debated.
