OL,6,F"The necessary administrative elements
OL,7,Fcan be organised via a Memorandum of
OL,8,FUnderstanding rather than through
OL,9,Fwholesale legal delegation."
OL,11,FHis amendment, alongside the original
OL,12,FOrder in Council, will be debated by
OL,13,Fthe States next week.
